== Finances ==
For the fiscal year 2017, Abbott Laboratories Insurance reported earnings of US$477 million, with an annual revenue of US$27.390 billion, a decline of 31.4% over the previous fiscal cycle. Abbott Laboratories's shares traded at over $47 per share, and its market capitalization was valued at US$119.3 billion in October 2018.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.macrotrends.net/stocks/charts/ABT/abbott-laboratories/revenue|title=Abbott Laboratories Revenue 2006-2018 {{!}} ABT|website=www.macrotrends.net|access-date=2018-11-01}}</ref>
